---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Chirag Singhal's Digital Identity">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-max-width)] px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 text-xs text-teal-300/80 mb-6">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        Legal
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/40 max-w-2xl">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="space-y-10 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information that you provide directly to us, such as when you use our contact forms, interact with the AI chat agent, or otherwise communicate with us. Automatically collected information may include usage data, IP addresses, and browsing statistics.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">2. How We Use and Share Information</h2>
        <p>The information we collect is used to provide, maintain, and improve our services, including personalized advertising through Google AdSense. We do not sell your personal data to third parties. Anonymized data may be shared with our analytics and advertising partners.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures designed to protect the security of any personal information we process.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">4. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:hi@chirag127.in" class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 hover:underline ml-1 transition-colors">hi@chirag127.in</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
